txt.en: 'This intrusion must be punished!'
'My pet! You killed my pet! Now you'll die!'
'Orcs are fighting us in the tunnels! Orcs from the north!'
'Great Goblin! The Orcs, the Orcs are fighting us!'
'Orcs are fighting in the tunnel!'
'Great Goblin! The Orcs from the north...they are fighting!'
'The Orcs in the depths are fighting us! The emissary is here to enslave us all!'
'Great Goblin, there are problems in the pits. The Orcs are fighting us.'
'Quit your sniveling, wretch. I know why they are here.'
'Come closer. Let us see if you are worthy of my notice! Attack them!'
'Servant of Angmar and Lugbûrz, I am here to call you to us.'
'Fools, thinking they command Ashúrz -- the Great Goblin!'
'You come before me in my own hall and speak of servitude?'
'Do you think the goblins of Goblin-town are fools!?'
'Bring the emissary forward!'
'You talk of service to Angmar, but Angmar is still weak. You come to us for aid.'
'We will not bend knee to Angmar. The goblins of Goblin-town bend only to Lugbûrz!'
'Goblin, this talk is foolish. It is pointless. We are the army of Angmar.'
'Madness? Madness? You fool!'
'To defy our might and our strength is...madness!'
'This is Goblin-town!'
'No!'
'I am just the messenger!'
'How could you! You killed Horm!'
'Angmar's call cannot be ignored. We will strike down all foes and blot out the light of the Sun.'
'Goblin, I am here to invite you to the slaughter. The North is strong!'
